title: Put God First In Your Life | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Put God First In Your Life | Victoria Osteen
description:
It’s easy to allow the busyness of life to overwhelm us. But being busy is not the same thing as being productive. When you let go of the distractions and prioritize spending time with God, He will direct your path and crown your efforts with success.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
